item.title: getting started
item.description: getting started with gohugo-amps This Hugo theme is supposed to be a starter theme to make it easy to adapt to Google’s AMP-Project. Included in the theme are 40+ shortcodes and partials making it a pleasure to embed AMP-Elements within your content files or your template. Installation Go to the directory where you have your Hugo site and run: $ mkdir themes $ cd themes $ git clone https://github.com/wildhaber/gohugo-amp.git $ rm -rf gohugo-amp/.
